snippet.description:
Special thanks to Con Man Games & SmashGames for providing us with the game and the codes to give out!

We are giving away game codes to FOUR lucky Theorists! 
Email us at teamtheorist@gmail.com with the name of your favorite Kindergarten character for the chance to WIN!

It is finally time to play Kindergarten 2! We've been waiting for this game to come out since we got to play the demo last year. Join us as we return to the playground and, of course, Nugget!

Find the game here ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1067850/Kindergarten_2/

Watch us play the first game! ► https://bit.ly/2CxizTk
